headline: Exiger CMO Kody Gurfein Wins PRNews' Top Women Award
summary: Exiger, the market-leading supply chain AI company and largest provider of supply chain technology to the U.S. Federal Government, today announced that Chief Marketing Officer Kody Gurfein has been named an honoree in PRNEWS' 2025 Class of Top Women, which includes executives from DoorDash, ESPN, Google DeepMind, Lenovo and Merck.
